&lt;p&gt;This role is to support the Trauma and Orthopaedic (T&amp;O) service at the Royal London Hospital, joining the T&amp;O admin team to support with the day to day operation of the Virtual Fracture Clinic. The successful candidate will be working in a fast paced environment, and is expected to be enthusiastic, conscientious, and have excellent time management and typing skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be working with clinicians, managers and admin staff across the Trust to ensure patients receive excellent quality care. Informal discussions are encouraged and you are invited to contact Preeta Varghese, Service Delivery Manager (Preeta.varghese@nhs.net) and/or Syed Muhin Hussain, Senior Patient Care Coordinator (syedmuhin.hussain@nhs.net) for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
